# C99 style for VaniaVolpe. The codebase already follows LLVM style (two-space
# indent, 80-column, right-aligned pointers, attached braces); the keys below are
# made explicit so the intent is self-documenting. Run `make format` to apply.
BasedOnStyle: LLVM
IndentWidth: 2
ColumnLimit: 80
PointerAlignment: Right
